snippet.title: Namokaar Channels Pvt Ltd
snippet.description:
Our channel under the Name and Logo of Namokaar Channels Pvt .Ltd has been created with an intention of promoting Hindi and Urdu Languages . We constantly strive  to inculcate love and interest amongst today's generation  for Hindi and Urdu  poetry. Thus , we are making fair use of the copyrighted materials.
 Moreover ,all the videos have been recorded and uploaded with the due consent of the Poets , Poetesses and Kavi sammelan organisers .

We don't claim any right over the literary work of any person  but we retains the  right to upload and share the videos of the events recorded by us on our official social media accounts.
